headline: Is Another Big Special Dividend Coming Up for Costco Wholesale Investors in December?
summary: Over the years, Costco Wholesale (NASDAQ: COST) investors have become accustomed to collecting special dividends when the company has a strong year.  Should investors expect another special dividend payment from Costco this year?  Last year, Costco announced a special dividend of $15 per share, which coincided with the release of its first-quarter results.
